headline: Capstone Partners & IMAP Release 2024-2025 Trends in Global M&A Research Survey:
summary: Capstone Partners, a leading middle market investment banking firm, in conjunction with its partner IMAP, a leading global investment banking advisory firm, released its annual Trends in Global M&A Survey Report, with insights from M&A advisors across the world.
